            <p>Boechari (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:Boechari1985-1986_01"/><citedRange>103-107</citedRange></bibl>) contains new reading, then followed almost precisely by Hasan Djafar (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:HasanDjafar1991_01"/><citedRange>10-11</citedRange></bibl>).</p> 
            <p>Re-edited here by Aditia Gunawan &amp; Arlo Griffiths from the photos of the plate, kindly made available to us by Terrylia Feisrami.</p>
